      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - Individuals/ societies/ self-help groups/ associations/ reservoir monopolies/ private units etc. involved in inland fisheries activities can avail the benefits of inland schemes.\n  - The applicant should be a Fisherman.\n  - Applicant should be above 18 years of age.\n  - Applicant must have own private land/leased land to avail new pond construction assistance for fish farming (In case of two or more land holders consent form of other land holders must be submitted).\n  - The beneficiary fisherman must have his own bank account.\n\n",
